data.description: Welcome to a serene retreat nestled in the heart of Sun City, the prestigious Del Webb 55 & older community in Georgetown, TX. This immaculate home, situated on a peaceful cul-de-sac, is the epitome of comfort and tranquility designed for those who appreciate a blend of elegance and low-maintenance living. As you step inside, you're greeted by an interior that radiates pristine cleanliness and an airy ambiance, with spaces meticulously designed for relaxation and entertainment. The open floor plan seamlessly connects living areas. The heart of this home, the kitchen, is equipped with a gas range, refrigerator, modern appliances, ample storage, and granite countertops, making it a joy for both casual meals and sophisticated gatherings. The living spaces have great natural light. Escape to the outdoors where beauty and privacy converge in the meticulously landscaped backyard. A highlight of this residence is the large screened-in patio, offering a serene oasis for morning coffees, evening cocktails, or simply soaking in the tranquility of your surroundings. This space ensures a bug-free environment to enjoy the Texas breeze and the beautifully designed outdoor setting.This home's location within the Del Webb community adds unparalleled value, with access to amenities that cater exclusively to the 55 and older demographic. Enjoy social and recreational activities, fitness centers, pools, and more, fostering a vibrant and active lifestyle.This property is not just a home; it's a lifestyle offering privacy, luxury, and community. Don't miss the opportunity to own this gem in Georgetown's most coveted 55+ community.?This description aims to capture the beauty and unique qualities of the home while emphasizing the lifestyle benefits of the Del Webb community.
